{"tid":466081,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「嬲撚死」應唔應該告佢好？","createTime":"2017-11-12T08:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T14:35:48.000Z","uid":72796,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2246cf4059d8e613363e28438612a34d9cc7c6","tid":466081,"uid":72796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:21:40.000Z","msg":"話說上星期去日本玩，回程就係飛機上面買左隻smartwatch ，因為本身血壓唔穩定一直想買隻錶睇血壓，所以見佢有咪順便買埋。<br />\n<br />\n點知返到屋企打開先知中伏，跟足說明書又充足電但都開唔到，跟手上網check間公司諗住去整，先發覺原來間公司已經汁撚左好耐，想問下大家，飛航公司賣啲已經倒閉左嘅公司產品有冇罪？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 告到間飛航公司都汁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買之前唔check清楚抵撚死<br />\n<br />\nBtw有冇律師大大知告唔告到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9f99e1109a19e9610c9e28711cbee8aaa2382e","tid":466081,"uid":72796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，買左間汁粒公司啲貨就搵客笨黎散貨，正一仆街黎"},{"pid":"c4285cbf71269f7c42a39ebc3eb8deb1dca1fe59","tid":466081,"uid":72796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"去客服投訴啲部門個個都射波，正一垃圾公司"},{"pid":"56da8083024c57def00d7d61247235b5d0d4afa3","tid":466081,"uid":55614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"投你老母票"},{"pid":"ca74916918a8873d41e3787890247d46feb5a8dd","tid":466081,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"飛航公司係乜?"},{"pid":"9d45d378b29bbc746650800bf8c4da04902ddd4d","tid":466081,"uid":78322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:31:51.000Z","msg":"汁你老"},{"pid":"31f553ff5bd85035fb64e533b576f2d5b440e374","tid":466081,"uid":37661,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"汁你老母粒<br />\n<br />\n你老母賣粒粒橙汁。"},{"pid":"d47362860244997a6f6d72b892